{"id":"remaliah","term":"Remaliah","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Adorned by the Lord, the father of Pekah, who conspired successfully against Pekahiah (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Kings 15:25\">2 Kings 15:25</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Kings 15:27\">27</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Kings 15:30\">30</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Kings 15:32\">32</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Kings 15:37\">37</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Isaiah 7:1\">Isa. 7:1</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Isaiah 7:4\">4</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Isaiah 7:5\">5</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 1:9\">9</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 8:6\">8:6</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["2 Kings 15:25","2 Kings 15:27","2 Kings 15:30","2 Kings 15:32","2 Kings 15:37","Isaiah 7:1","Isaiah 7:4","Isaiah 7:5","Genesis 1:9","Genesis 8:6"]}